	Given User provided valid Id '<id>'  and '<name>'for hotel 
	And Use has added required details for hotel
	When User calls AddHotel api
	Then Hotel with name '<name>' should be present in the response
Examples: 
| id | name   |
| 1  | hotel1 |
| 2  | hotel2 |
| 3  | hotel3 |

